                <h2>How Can We Help You?</h2>
                <p>Welcome to Harfy support. We're here to help you with your Quran learning journey.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I start learning?</h3>
                    <p>After signing up, you'll receive a 7-day free trial. Simply select a Surah from the list, choose a verse, and begin your interactive learning session with word-by-word translation and practice.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What's included in the free trial?</h3>
                    <p>Your 7-day free trial includes full access to all features: word-by-word learning, interactive practice sessions, progress tracking, and all 114 Surahs of the Quran.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How does the subscription work?</h3>
                    <p>After your free trial, you can choose between monthly ($9.99/month) or yearly ($59.99/year) subscriptions. You can manage or cancel your subscription anytime through your device's Settings app.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How can I track my progress?</h3>
                    <p>Your progress is automatically tracked for each verse you practice. Green indicates mastered verses (80%+ accuracy), blue for good progress (60-80%), and yellow for verses that need more practice.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Can I practice offline?</h3>
                    <p>Yes! Once verses are loaded, you can practice offline. Your progress will sync when you reconnect to the internet.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I restore my purchase?</h3>
                    <p>If you've already subscribed, tap "Restore Purchases" on the subscription screen to restore your access.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I cancel my subscription?</h3>
                    <p>You can cancel anytime through your device settings: Settings > [Your Name] > Subscriptions > Harfy > Cancel Subscription.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I delete my account?</h3>
                    <p>You can delete your account from within the app: Settings > Account > Delete Account. This will permanently remove all your data and progress.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
                <div class="troubleshooting">
                    <p><strong>App not loading properly?</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Check your internet connection</li>
                        <li>Force quit and restart the app</li>
                        <li>Update to the latest version from the App Store</li>
                        <li>Try signing out and signing back in</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top: 20px;"><strong>Subscription issues?</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Ensure you're signed into the correct Apple ID</li>
                        <li>Check your subscription status in Settings</li>
                        <li>Try "Restore Purchases" in the app</li>
                        <li>Contact us if the problem persists</li>
